365
00:29:52,051 --> 00:29:54,581
♪I believe love can turn♪

366
00:29:54,581 --> 00:29:57,911
♪A thousand possibilities♪

367
00:29:58,151 --> 00:30:01,491
♪Hold you tighter by a fraction♪

368
